5. Credit System

Types:

A. Deposit Credit
	•	earned from contribution

B. Borrow Credit
	•	temporarily locked when checking out

C. Reputation Modifier
	•	adjusts future valuations

⸻

Important Rule:

Credits are backed by real inventory

No inflation.

